          <p class='first-para'>
            I should tell the Committee that the sound system is not working properly, though I am happy to report that it has been getting through to <span class="italic">Hansard</span> upstairs. So nothing has been lost in that respect. As you will observe, however, the lights are not coming on. If the noble Lord, Lord Kingsland, could wait to let us know what he has decided to do with this
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_378gc' title='Col. 378GC &mdash; HL Deb 24 February 2005 vol 669 c378GC' name='column_378gc' href='#column_378gc' rel='bookmark'>378GC</a>
            amendment, it will give them a chance to make some adjustments. I am assured that it will take less than half a minute.
