        <span class="italic">[The Sitting was suspended from 4.48 to 4.50 p.m.]</span>
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0669P0-04434'>
        <a name='S5LV0669P0_20050224_GCR_68'>  </a>
        <blockquote class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <cite class='member author entry-title unmatched-member'>The Deputy Chairman of Committees</cite>
