      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0669P0-04457'>
        <a name='S5LV0669P0_20050224_GCR_91'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-christopher-prout' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0669P0_20050224_GCR_91' title='Link to this speech by Mr Christopher Prout' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-christopher-prout" title="Mr Christopher Prout">Lord Kingsland</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
