      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0669P0-04475'>
        <a name='S5LV0669P0_20050224_GCR_109'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-jan-simon' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0669P0_20050224_GCR_109' title='Link to this speech by Mr Jan Simon' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-jan-simon" title="Mr Jan Simon">The Deputy Chairman of Committees (Viscount Simon)</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            In calling Amendment No. 39, I must advise noble Lords that if this amendment is agreed to, I shall not be able to call Amendment No. 40 by reason of pre-emption.
          </p>
