      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0669P0-04521'>
        <a name='S5LV0669P0_20050224_GCR_155'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-peter-goldsmith' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0669P0_20050224_GCR_155' title='Link to this speech by Mr Peter Goldsmith' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-peter-goldsmith" title="Mr Peter Goldsmith">Lord Goldsmith</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I suggest this may be a convenient moment for the Committee to adjourn and to continue consideration of the remaining few groupings on Wednesday 2 March at 3.30 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0669P0-04522'>
        <a name='S5LV0669P0_20050224_GCR_156'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-jan-simon' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0669P0_20050224_GCR_156' title='Link to this speech by Mr Jan Simon' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-jan-simon" title="Mr Jan Simon">The Deputy Chairman of Committees (Viscount Simon)</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The Committee stands adjourned until Wednesday at 3.30 p.m.</p><p>
            The Committee adjourned at one minute past seven o'clock.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
